data.description: This bright 3/2 garden home in the Creekside Addition features a split bedroom floor plan with an open concept kitchen/dining/living room, perfect for entertaining. Off of the dining room is a covered porch. Near the kitchen is an attached two car garage. This home is close to Tally Elementary and is in an excellent location, convenient to shopping, restaurants and Peterson Hospital. Water heater approx. 1.5 years old, HVAC approx. 2.5 years old, roof approx. 3-4 years old.
